column2: "You're not going to look any further than that?"
"These parts be swarmin' wi' sea beasties. If we strike out too far, we'll be fish food. D'ye want that?"

"It's okay.
<%me> and I are here, so we should be able to manage."
"Aye, wi' someone other than you 'ere we might stand a chance."
"We weren't doin' nothin'! Why's it comin' after us?!"
"Arr, that be Camarotz! What in blazes is he doin' up there?!"
"Maybe he got lost? It doesn't matter why he's there, you need to go help him!"
"We'll take care of the enemy! While we're doing that, you get over there!"
"Dangerous or not, at times like this, you have to act!"
